{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"562","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"國內金融業者挺綠能 投入1.2兆元","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2019-11-07 03:56 </span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>經濟日報 記者葉憶如、王奐敏／台北報導</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>國內金融機構配合政府政策挺綠色能源，最新統計包括銀行授信、保險投資與證券募資，各投入<span lang='EN-US'>1.1</span>兆、<span lang='EN-US'>140</span>億元及<span lang='EN-US'>738</span>億元，合計近<span lang='EN-US'>1.2</span>兆元，金管會主委顧立雄昨（<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>）日表示，未來透過鼓勵金融機構專案融資、直接投資或是在資本市場籌資，讓綠能資金逐步到位。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>櫃買中心昨日舉辦「<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>台北綠色債券國際研討會」，顧立雄致詞表示，近年積極發展綠色金融，據金管會統計今年<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>月底為止，銀行對綠能科技產業放款餘額超過新台幣<span lang='EN-US'>1.1</span>兆元，保險業資金獲准投資八家再生能源電廠，加計<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>月核准投資風力發電<span lang='EN-US'>42</span>億元，金額合計達<span lang='EN-US'>140</span>億。證券募資方面，台灣綠色債券市場自<span lang='EN-US'>2017</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>5</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>19</span>日由玉山、凱基、中國信託及永豐等四家銀行發行國內首批綠色債券以來，今年<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>月底，綠色債券共計發行<span lang='EN-US'>32</span>檔、<span lang='EN-US'>738</span>億，國內金融業為挺綠能，總計已投入約<span lang='EN-US'>1.18</span>兆元資金。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>櫃買中心董事長陳永誠表示，我國綠色債券市場至今雖僅發展兩年半時間，總發行規模已達新台幣<span lang='EN-US'>738</span>億元，預估今年底累計發行總額可望突破新台幣<span lang='EN-US'>1,000</span>億元，可見綠色債券平台是連結資本市場與綠色產業的溝通橋梁。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://money.udn.com/money/story/5613/4149221</span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-11-08","clk_count":"94"}},"__N_SSG":true}